text:
Thanks a TON for helping me find
a spot for my tent. It's a PERFECT
starting spot for all my morning,
afternoon, and even my evening
jogs. I got you a small something
to say thanks. Try it on!

I'm serious about attracting some
top-tier, first-round-draft-pick,
intramural all-star neighboring
talent. Here's the thing I said
I was gonna send you. Now go
flex that decorating muscle!
